        <div class="col-md-8 about-content">
            <h2 class="mb-3">About Our Clinic</h2>
            <p>
                Our clinic is dedicated to providing compassionate and comprehensive care for your beloved pets. We understand the importance of your pet's health and well-being, and our team of experienced veterinarians and staff are committed to delivering the highest quality service.
